{"tid":2436116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聰聰：美國聽證會預告","createTime":"2021-03-06T23:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T15:00:52.000Z","uid":263150,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"613c8bb661b1a4579804e75d91c4b8bd47b3568a","tid":2436116,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T23:29:06.000Z","msg":"【🔔美國聽證會預告：講述全球民主的現況 遏止中共威權擴張】<br />\n<br />\n在香港抗爭運動和全球民主陷入僵局之際，港人必須在國際層面持續發聲，令各國更清楚中共極權的禍害，著手以具體有效的行動遏止中共的威權擴張。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVow3qC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVow3qC.jpg&h=44434474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就此，我將會於下星期的美國參議院外交事務委員會作證，出席名為「全球民主的現況」（The State of Democracy around the world）的聽證會。我已<span class=\"red\">累積出席超過五次的美國國會聽證會</span>，但是次聽證會的關注和規模都相對龐大，在消息傳出後已收到不少在人權組織的朋友鼓勵，亦會比以往花更多時間準備。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">作為聽證會唯一的港人代表</span>，我深深明白責任之重，也更渴望將香港與全球民主的困局清晰易明地呈現世人眼前。在聽證中，我將會講述近月中共對香港公民社會以及制度的破壞，以及強調民主社會必須制訂鞏固全球民主的議程、時間表以及行動。若各位想事先了解一下我對如何守護全球民主的想法，可以先參考這篇我於《外交政策》發表的文章（<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/.../china-us-democracy.../\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F...%2Fchina-us-democracy...%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bE63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=41fb9068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/.../china-us-democracy.../</a>）。<br />\n<br />\n🔈美國參議院外交事務委員會聽證：<br />\n<br />\nThe State of Democracy Around the World<br />\n「全球民主的現況」<br />\n<br />\n首輪聽證嘉賓：<br />\nThe Honorable Madeleine Albright 前美國國務卿<br />\nAmbassador Paula J. Dobriansky 前美國國際事務副秘書長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次輪聽證嘉賓：<br />\nMr. Peter Biar Ajak, PhD 南蘇丹民運人士<br />\nWai Hnin Pwint Thon 緬甸民運人士<br />\nNathan Law<br />\n<br />\n時間：3月10日 美東時間早上10點 香港時間晚上11點<br />\n<br />\n詳情及直播連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3e9j3FU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3e9j3FU&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bE63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=2e80fdaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3e9j3FU</a>"},{"pid":"e2bf95e920712a28d24aeb5404b9249d9708ec40","tid":2436116,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3279842625f7ac9bc3d12ebb931e20d30abec661","tid":2436116,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T23:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9896237dc42387b3681b1a5afb56dc5b2fe165","tid":2436116,"uid":55379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea441d77eabb28a5344fbcbb38663b87309669d","tid":2436116,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20fde2805eb29f159f57d8c3b0a8db07b34915d","tid":2436116,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"國務卿唔見搵肥仔奧"},{"pid":"6e83c359cc3d8bc6f9ae0e8087ae862541ef3c0d","tid":2436116,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"諗起佢上次 講建民主中國 <br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔好再講<br />\n<br />\n好反感"},{"pid":"93c71ec5c20d2e4381dc44dbdc4ca158913d9518","tid":2436116,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5392eef56e5aaf4eeb8f94fc408fd0cba0c5adc4","tid":2436116,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}